Description:
RealTime Architect - software for professional design landscape in 2D and 3D. Provides the ability to create dendroplan, reliefs,
 three-dimensional images of objects, as well as the effect of real travel in the territory. You will create dendroplan, 
kind of land with a bird's eye view, 3D-image area with the possibility of movement on the territory, the creation of videoprikoly. 
Version 2013 contains about 200 objects in the Ultra-resolution, 16,400 objects, 6,900 exclusive of planning and 3,100 attributes of design.
 The program site has an impressive photo gallery of finished projects and screenshots of the program and view a short video design 
works created by RealTime Architect
